<template>
  <cus-wraper>
    <template>
      <el-form
        :model="form"
        :rules="rules"
        ref="dataForm"
        label-width="100px"
        class="demo-ruleForm"
      >
        <el-form-item>
          <el-button  size="mini" type="primary" @click="submitForm('form')">下一步</el-button>
        </el-form-item>
      </el-form>
    </template>
  </cus-wraper>
</template>
<script>
import {
  addRuleMain,
  deleteRuleMain,
  updateRuleMain
} from "@/api/ibrms/ruleMain";
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      tabPosition: "right",
      form: {
        state: "0",
        region: "",
        date1: "",
        date2: "",
        delivery: false,
        type: [],
        resource: "",
        desc: ""
      },
      //检验规则
      rules: {
        userCode: [
          {
            required: true,
            message: this.$t("ruleMessageInfoBom.xxx"),
            trigger: "blur"
          }
        ]
      }
    };
  },
  computed: {},
  created() {},
  methods: {
    submitForm(formName) {
      this.$refs[formName].validate(valid => {
        if (valid) {
          alert("submit!");
        } else {
          console.log("error submit!!");
          return false;
        }
      });
    },
    resetForm(formName) {
      this.$refs[formName].resetFields();
    }
  }
};
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
.el-select {
  width: 100%;
}
</style>
